      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"worth\" doesn't pay back millions in debt. everyone i know expects me to be this huge success, and now i'm just the guy who crashed and burned. the shame is constant. it's like every time i breathe, i'm just reminding everyone of how much i messed up. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling of being a disappointment is to just... not be here anymore. it feels more logical than trying to live a life of pure embarrassment.",
