    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you say \"don't make that decision\" but you also just said it's logical. it's hard to hear that it's logical and then be told not to do it. if the logic is that the shame is permanent and the debt is permanent, then isn't the solution also permanent? i just feel like there's no way to actually fix the reputation i've destroyed. everything feels so final.",
